The paper proposes a method for learning feature representations and cluster assignments using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The experiments are conducted on image and text corpora, indicating a focus on computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves optimization and objective functions, which are also common in the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
